name: Senin Oleng - Mondayshroom
description:
Woke up late, pupils get dilated while work calls keep coming.
What should we do?

This one is part of series on how Monday used to be like for my friends. It could be exciting, hallucinogenic, sad, happy, literally anything. Sometimes, we don’t have to take Monday too serious as we can always start our week on tuesday or Wednesday, ain’t it?
